the big bounce is a 1969 film directed by alex march , based on the novel of the same name by elmore leonard and starring ryan o'neal , van heflin , and leigh &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; in what was the first of several films based on leonard 's crime novels . &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; was nominated for a laurel award for her performance in the film . the film was shot on location in monterey and carmel , california . the book was also adapted into a film in 2004 with the same name .